skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: oxford vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Oxford, Mississippi, near the Ole Miss Campus. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Oxford Vegan ." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Oxford Vegan for a fact.
